.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-DASHBOARD-GET 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.9.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-dashboard\-get \- Get one live dashboard into an API\-safe local JSON draft.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util dashboard get [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Get one live dashboard into an API\-safe local JSON draft.
.PP
Use this when you need a local copy of one live dashboard for review, patching, cloning, or later publish work.
.SH COMMON OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-dashboard\-uid
live Grafana dashboard UID to fetch.
.TP
.B \-\-output
write the fetched draft to this path.
.TP
.B Shared live flags
\-\-url, \-\-token, \-\-basic\-user, \-\-basic\-password, \-\-profile.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Get one live dashboard into an API\-safe local JSON draft.
.EX
grafana-util dashboard get --profile prod --dashboard-uid cpu-main --output ./cpu-main.json
.EE
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBgrafana-util\fR(1),
\fBgrafana-util-dashboard\fR(1)
